            <div type="a">
                <column>04</column>
                <head>The True Doctrine</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>James W. Gerard of New York, an old Whig, claims that the true Republican
                    doctrine is not to prevent the spread of slavery to the territories, but to
                    abolish slavery in the South.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
